ZH: 我们一起去餐厅用餐吧。
EN: Let's go to the restaurant together for a meal.
ZH: 请问这家餐厅用餐需要预约吗？
EN: Do we need a reservation to dine at this restaurant?
ZH: 今天晚上我不用餐，谢谢。
EN: I won't be dining tonight, thank you.
ZH: 在中国，用餐时要用筷子而不是刀叉。
EN: In China, we use chopsticks instead of knives and forks for dining.
ZH: 昨天晚上我们在家用餐。
EN: We dined at home last night.
ZH: 不要在工作区域用餐。
EN: Don't eat in the work area.
ZH: 请注意，禁止在图书馆内用餐。
EN: Please note that dining is forbidden inside the library.
ZH: 医院内禁止用餐。
EN: Dining is not allowed inside the hospital.
ZH: 每天用餐时，我们应该尽量避免使用手机。
EN: During meals, we should try to avoid using our phones as much as possible.
ZH: 请在规定的时间内用餐。
EN: Please dine within the designated time.
ZH: 这个餐厅提供免费的自助用餐。
EN: This restaurant offers free buffet dining.
ZH: 我们公司每天都会提供午餐用餐食物。
EN: Our company provides lunch meals every day.
ZH: 我们一起到公园野餐用餐吧。
EN: Let's have a picnic together at the park for our meal.
ZH: 我们可以一边欣赏美景，一边用餐。
EN: We can dine while enjoying the beautiful scenery.
ZH: 学校规定学生只能在食堂用餐。
EN: The school regulations state that students can only dine in the cafeteria.
ZH: 我们可以自带食物在酒店房间用餐。
EN: We can bring our own food and dine in the hotel room.
ZH: 请不要在卧室内用餐。
EN: Please refrain from dining in the bedroom.
ZH: 我们可以在露天的餐厅用餐。
EN: We can dine at the open-air restaurant.
ZH: 在我家的周年纪念日，我会为你准备一顿特别的用餐。
EN: On our anniversary, I will prepare a special dining experience for you at my house.
ZH: 商务会议之后，我们将安排大家用餐。
EN: We will arrange a meal for everyone after the business meeting.
ZH: 周末我们一家人都会一起用餐。
EN: We always have meals together as a family on weekends.
